Dependencies
============

Debian packages
---------------

ocaml-native-compilers
ocaml-findlib
camlp4-extra
libpcre-ocaml-dev
libextlib-ocaml-dev
libocamlnet-ocaml-dev
libzip-ocaml-dev
libocsigen-xhtml-ocaml-dev
libounit-ocaml-dev

libevent-dev
libcurl4-gnutls-dev (with c-ares enabled, from sigpwr repo)

Other
-----

ocaml-event git://repo.or.cz/ocaml-event.git
ocurl git://repo.or.cz/ocurl.git branch event
extunix http://git.ocamlcore.org/extunix/extunix.git


What should be installed on Debian:
------

aptitude install ocaml-native-compilers
aptitude install ocaml-findlib
aptitude install camlp4-extra
aptitude install libpcre-ocaml-dev
aptitude install libextlib-ocaml-dev
aptitude install libocamlnet-ocaml-dev
aptitude install libzip-ocaml-dev
aptitude install libocsigen-xhtml-ocaml-dev
aptitude install libounit-ocaml-dev
aptitude install libevent-dev
aptitude install libcurl4-gnutls-dev #(with c-ares enabled, from sigpwr repo)
aptitude install xfslibs-dev
aptitude install liblzo2-dev
aptitude install libsnappy-dev
aptitude install libgoogle-perftools-dev
aptitude install libboost-thread-dev
aptitude install libboost-iostreams-dev
aptitude install libfileutils-ocaml-dev
aptitude install libjson-wheel-ocaml-dev
aptitude install libjson-static-camlp4-dev
aptitude install libodn-ocaml
aptitude install libodn-ocaml-dev
aptitude install ocamlmod
aptitude install ocamlify
aptitude install libcurl-ocaml
aptitude install libcurl-ocaml-dev
aptitude install subversion
aptitude install apt-file
apt-file update 

